# Note: requirements.lock is NOT ignored - it should be committed
# Workflow:
# - Developers: Edit requirements.txt, then run `uv pip compile requirements.txt -o requirements.lock`
# - Users: Install from lock file with `uv pip install -r requirements.lock`

